title: Serendipity Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, European, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Focus is on local, organic non-gmo, and seasonal ingredients. Lunch menu has soups, sandwiches, salads, thin-crust pizza, appetizers, and snacks. Kitchen is willing to modify a dish to make it vegan and/or gluten free. Also offers vegan and gluten free baked goods.
